title: How many homeless in San Francisco? Not as many as it might seem
description: It may not seem like it, but there are fewer homeless people on the streets of San Francisco now than there were in 2004. So why is homelessness often regarded as being worse than ever?
seo_title: San Francisco's homeless problem: Fewer on the streets than it might seem
author: Kevin Fagan, Lea Suzuki, John Blanchard, Emma O'Neill, and Audrey DeBruine
twitter_text: How many homeless in San Francisco? Not as many as you might think. So why do things seem worse than ever?
